The paper discusses a machine learning as a service (MLaaS) platform, which is primarily related to the field of machine learning (cs.LG). The platform also involves collaboration and management of data and models, which falls under the categories of distributed computing (cs.DC) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also mentions the deployment of commercial services, which is related to computer engineering (cs.CE). Finally, the paper discusses visualization tools for analyzing work, which is related to computer vision (cs.CV).
